Four undescribed flavonol glycosides, igdoside A-D (
2–5
), and four known glucosides (
1, 6–8
) (
Fig. 1
) were isolated from the ethyl acetate and 
n
-butanol extracts.

In addition, four known flavonol glycosides (
Fig. 1
), namely 
transtiliroside
(
1
) (
Kumarasamy et al., 2003
), isorhamnetin-3- 
O -β
-D-galactopyranoside (
6
) (
Wang et al., 2013
), astragalin (
7
) (
Ghavam-Haghi and Dinani, 2017
), and isorhamnetin-3- 
O -β
-D-galactopyranosyl-7- 
O -α
-L-rhamnopyranoside (
8
) (
Liu et al., 2009
, 
2017
; 
Roesch et al., 2004
) were identified by comparing their NMR and/or LC-MS data to previously reported values. Notably, this is the first instance of isolation of compound 
8
from this species.
